Jonathon Stevenson was just 16 years old when he wrote a letter to Richie Benaud for advice on left-handed leg spin . 
  He shared the letter on Twitter in the wake of the cricket legend's death . 
  Accompanying the letter was a full sheet of notes about spin bowling for left-hand bowlers . 
  Benaud passed away in his sleep on Thursday night after battling skin cancer . 
 